---
title: Bacon Rigatoni all’Arrabbiata with Chives and Garlic Ciabatta
description: This Bacon Rigatoni all’Arrabbiata is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
